# dismissModal

**Instance Method**

Dismisses the document displayed in modal view.

## Declaration

```swift
void dismissModal();
```

## Discussion

When the document is dismissed, the previous document is brought into focus.

## Overlaying Document

- **presentModal**: Displays the passed document on top of the current document.
